                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>amount must appear in your Occident, please not to<lb/> mention my name in no shape\n                nor form—only say Re-<lb/>-ceived from <persName>Rosalta</persName> and nothing\n                more.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Please receive my very best wishes, and believe me,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Dear sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours, Respectfully.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
